i.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/4549","id":289671735,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDI4OTY3MTczNQ==","user":{"login":"javaddict","id":6240021,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYyNDAwMjE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6240021?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict","html_url":"https://github.com/javaddict","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2017-03-28T06:00:40Z","updated_at":"2017-03-28T10:37:20Z","body":"Yes! I have been running into the same situation recently.\r\nIt is very unpredictable and hard to reproduce. I finally nail it at its last appearance.\r\n\r\nThe cause is that the execution of `dispose()` in\r\n`com.badlogic.gdx.utils.Timer.TimerThread` should have set `instance` to null but\r\nsomehow it is found not null. I don't know how could this happen because the line\r\nbefore it `Gdx.app.removeLifecycleListener(this);` is executed. (because `resume()`\r\nand `pause()` not called anymore)\r\nSo next time when `Timer.schedule(...)` is called, the constructor of `TimerThread`\r\nis not executed, resulting that `Timer.instance()` just keep returning a dead instance\r\nwhich won't trigger any task on it.\r\n\r\nCurrently my workaround is to not initialize `instance` at the member declaration\r\nand add a public static method to clear `instance`. Every time `AndroidApplication`\r\ncreated and started, call this method to ensure that `instance` is null.","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/comments/289671735/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"javaddict","id":6240021,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYyNDAwMjE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6240021?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict","html_url":"https://github.com/javaddict","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/javaddict/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"id":1035356506,"node_id":"MDExOkNsb3NlZEV2ZW50MTAzNTM1NjUwNg==","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/events/1035356506","actor":{"login":"NathanSweet","id":434010,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQzNDAxMA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/434010?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet","html_url":"https://github.com/NathanSweet","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users